data.description: Beautiful 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom, 2 Car Garage Home in the Desirable Lake Charles Community in Saint Lucie West. Newer Stainless Appliances, New Quartz Countertops, Plantation Shutters, New Luxury Vinyl Flooring Throughout, Interior & Exterior Recently Painted, Accordion Shutters and Extended Re-Screened Patio with Views of the Preserve Area. The Community Offers Recreational Amenities Such as Heated Pool with Spa, Basketball, Tennis/Pickleball, Shuffleboard, Bocce and More! This Home is Move In Ready, Close to I-95, Mets Stadium and Shopping! Don't Miss this Opportunity!
